    • 方法详细资料

      • requestInputEventCapture

        public int requestInputEventCapture(int targetDisplayType,
                                    int[] inputTypes,
                                    int requestFlags,
                                    CarInputManager.CarInputCaptureCallback callback)
        Requests capturing of input event for the specified display for all requested input types.

        The request can fail if a high priority client is holding it. The client can set CAPTURE_REQ_FLAGS_ALLOW_DELAYED_GRANT in requestFlags to wait for the current high priority client to release it.

        If only some of the input types specified are available, the request will either:

        • fail, returning INPUT_CAPTURE_RESPONSE_FAILED, or
        • be deferred, returning INPUT_CAPTURE_RESPONSE_DELAYED, if the CAPTURE_REQ_FLAGS_ALLOW_DELAYED_GRANT flag is used.

        After INPUT_CAPTURE_RESPONSE_DELAYED is returned, no input types are captured until the client receives a CarInputManager.CarInputCaptureCallback.onCaptureStateChanged(int, int[]) call with valid input types.

        The targetDisplayType parameter must only contain driver display types (which are CarOccupantZoneManager.DISPLAY_TYPE_MAIN and CarOccupantZoneManager.DISPLAY_TYPE_INSTRUMENT_CLUSTER.

        Callbacks are grouped and stacked per display types. Only the most recently registered callback will receive the incoming events for the associated display and input types. For instance, if two callbacks are registered against the same display type, on the same CarInputManager instance, then only the last registered callback will receive events, even if they were registered for different input event types.

        参数:
        targetDisplayType - the display type to register callback for
        inputTypes - the input type to register callback for
        requestFlags - the capture request flag
        callback - the callback to receive the input events
        返回:
        the input capture response indicating if registration succeed, failed or delayed
        抛出:
        java.lang.SecurityException - if caller doesn't have one of the following permissions granted: android.car.permission.CAR_MONITOR_INPUT nor android.Manifest.permission.MONITOR_INPUT
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if targetDisplayType parameter correspond to a non supported display type
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if inputTypes parameter contains invalid or non supported values

      • requestInputEventCapture

        public int requestInputEventCapture(int targetDisplayType,
                                    int[] inputTypes,
                                    int requestFlags,
                                    java.util.concurrent.Executor executor,
                                    CarInputManager.CarInputCaptureCallback callback)
        Works just like requestInputEventCapture(int, int[], int, CarInputCaptureCallback) except that callbacks are invoked using the executor passed as parameter.
        参数:
        targetDisplayType - the display type to register callback against
        inputTypes - the input type to register callback against
        requestFlags - the capture request flag
        executor - Executor to handle the callbacks
        callback - the callback to receive the input events
        返回:
        the input capture response indicating if registration succeed, failed or delayed
        抛出:
        java.lang.SecurityException - if caller doesn't have one of the following permissions granted: android.car.permission.CAR_MONITOR_INPUT nor android.Manifest.permission.MONITOR_INPUT
        另请参阅:

      • injectKeyEvent

        public void injectKeyEvent(KeyEvent event,
                           int targetDisplayType)
        Injects the KeyEvent passed as parameter against Car Input API.

        The event parameter display id will be overridden accordingly to the display type also passed as parameter.

        参数:
        event - the key event to inject
        targetDisplayType - the display type associated with the key event
        抛出:
        RemoteException - in case of failure when invoking car input service

      • onCarDisconnected

        protected void onCarDisconnected()
        从类复制的说明: CarManagerBase
        Handle disconnection of car service (=crash). As car service has crashed already, this call should only clean up any listeners / callbacks passed from client. Clearing object passed to car service is not necessary as car service has crashed. Note that Car*Manager will not work any more as all binders are invalid. Client should re-create all Car*Managers when car service is restarted.
        指定者:
        onCarDisconnected 在类中 CarManagerBase
